{
  "texts": [
    "B.4 ADL-LLM w/o CoTThis approach differs from ADL-LLM only in the user prompt, where the \"Reason step by step\" instruction is omitted.",
    "B.4.1 System prompt.Act as a human activity recognition system that infers the activities performed by a subject in their home.",
    "The home has the following locations: 'dining room', 'hall', 'kitchen', 'living room', 'medicine area', 'office', and 'outside home'.",
    "The system captures the subject's interactions with chairs, couches, pantries, pots drawers, cutlery drawers, medicine cabinets, fridge, stove, and television.",
    "I will provide you with a description of what happened during a specific time window, and your goal is to provide the most likely activity."
  ]
}